  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t佢地話係潛伏係大陸既外國勢力喎   唔通佢哋認自己帶頭咩   衰嘢實屈香港人做，邊得似某啲香港人淨係識捅自己人幾刀<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9uYS5jeC9pL0RSNzFtN3UucG5n\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://na.cx/i/DR71m7u.png\">https://na.cx/i/DR71m7u.png</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmxpaC5rZy90aHVtYm5haWw_dT1odHRwcyUzQSUyRiUyRm5hLmN4JTJGaSUyRjlaeE15ZlgucG5nJmg9ODIwYTRiODgmcz01NDA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ZxMyfX.png&amp;h=820a4b88&amp;s=540\">https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ZxMyfX.png&amp;h=820a4b88&amp;s=540</a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n所以香港人根本唔需要出聲   買定花生就算數     由得牠們自生自滅   最怕佢哋主人收手   佢哋主人越癲越好<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmxpaC5rZy90aHVtYm5haWw_dT1odHRwcyUzQSUyRiUyRm5hLmN4JTJGaSUyRmg0UDNBemIucG5nJmg9NWJhZjVmNjImcz01NDA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh4P3Azb.png&amp;h=5baf5f62&amp;s=540\">https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh4P3Azb.png&amp;h=5baf5f62&amp;s=540</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmxpaC5rZy90aHVtYm5haWw_dT1odHRwcyUzQSUyRiUyRm5hLmN4JTJGaSUyRjZ3a3V2N00ucG5nJmg9Njk5YTcwNTcmcz01NDA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6wkuv7M.png&amp;h=699a7057&amp;s=540\">https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6wkuv7M.png&amp;h=699a7057&amp;s=540</a><br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmxpaC5rZy90aHVtYm5haWw_dT1odHRwcyUzQSUyRiUyRm5hLmN4JTJGaSUyRlU4NlFaOHQucG5nJmg9ODcxMDVkNTUmcz01NDA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU86QZ8t.png&amp;h=87105d55&amp;s=540\">https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU86QZ8t.png&amp;h=87105d55&amp;s=540</a><br/>\n